        <headline>Extreme Heat Warning issued August 8 at 1:21AM CDT until August 8 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Dangerously hot conditions with temperatures up to 110
expected.

* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon.

* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 8 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Heat related illnesses increase significantly during
extreme heat and high humidity events.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
